letter jackets to marching band?

22:05.658 --> 22:07.742
It's not a sport.

22:07.827 --> 22:09.160
We all know it.

22:09.245 --> 22:11.371
This kid is crazy.

22:11.455 --> 22:13.707
Mary Elizabeth,
I think you’re really gonna regret that...

22:13.791 --> 22:17.585
you know— haircut when you
look back at old photographs.

22:17.670 --> 22:19.921
