23:33.621 --> 23:36.289
I kinda wished he'd left a note.
You know what I mean?

23:43.464 --> 23:45.006
Where's the bathroom?

23:47.134 --> 23:48.176
It's up the stairs.

23:48.260 --> 23:49.552
Thanks, Sam.

23:49.637 --> 23:51.346
You're so nice.

24:04.318 --> 24:05.652
Charlie.

24:08.864 --> 24:10.031
Weird.

24:17.331 --> 24:18.331
Charlie.

24:18.415 --> 24:19.791
What...

24:20.835 --> 24:22.252
Who was that kid?

24:22.336 --> 24:24.796
Relax. Relax. He's a friend of mine.

24:25.381 --> 24:26.631
Stay here.

24:26.715 --> 24:28.383
I didn't see anything.

24:28.467 --> 24:30.677
Yeah, I know you saw something,
but it's okay.

24:31.595 --> 24:33.138
Okay, listen...

24:34.515 --> 24:36.432
Brad doesn't want anyone to know.

24:38.185 --> 24:39.310
Wait.

24:40.187 --> 24:43.231
- Are you baked?
- Like a cake.

24:43.315 --> 24:45.316
That's what Bob said.

24:45.401 --> 24:47.986
And you can't have three on a match
because then they'd find us.

24:48.070 --> 24:50.613
And everybody laughed
but I don't understand what's funny.

24:51.615 --> 24:55.034
Okay, Charlie, listen.

24:56.537 --> 24:58.454
I need you to promise...

24:58.539 --> 25:01.916
