to anyone about me and Brad.

25:03.127 --> 25:05.170
Okay? This has to be our little secret.

25:05.963 --> 25:09.215
Our little secret. Agreed.

25:10.092 --> 25:11.092
Okay.

25:11.177 --> 25:12.802
Thank you.

25:12.887 --> 25:14.012
We'll talk later.

25:16.849 --> 25:18.766
I look forward to that big talk.

25:21.770 --> 25:24.063
Can I have your cherry?

25:24.148 --> 25:27.775
Isn't this the best milk shake ever, Alice?

25:27.860 --> 25:29.444
It's even better than the first one.

25:35.284 --> 25:37.911
Charlie just told me that
his best friend shot himself.

25:41.081 --> 25:43.499
I don't think he has any friends.

25:50.758 --> 25:52.383
Hey, everyone!

25:52.468 --> 25:53.718
Everybody!

25:55.763 --> 25:58.389
Everyone...

25:58.474 --> 26:00.475
raise your glasses to Charlie.

26:02.478 --> 26:05.355
- What did I do?
- You didn't do anything.

26:05.439 --> 26:07.690
We just wanna toast to our new friend.

26:07.775 --> 26:09.359
You see things.

26:09.443 --> 26:11.069
And you understand.

26:12.738 --> 26:13.821
You're a wallflower.

26:17.618 --> 26:18.618
What is it? What's wrong?

26:20.246 --> 26:22.372
I didn't think anyone noticed me.

26:25.834 --> 26:29.045
Well, we didn't think
there was anyone cool left to meet.

26:29.129 --> 26:31.172
So come on, everyone.

26:33.425 --> 26:34.801
To Charlie.

26:34.885 --> 26:36.302
To Charlie.

26:40.599 --> 26:43.142
Welcome to the Island of Misfit Toys.

26:53.487 --> 26:55.321
My God! What is this song?

26:55.406 --> 26:56.948
Right? I have no idea.

26:57.032 --> 26:58.783
Have you ever heard this before?

26:59.368 --> 27:00.535
