27:05.624 --> 27:06.708
Patrick, It's the perfect song.

27:06.792 --> 27:09.043
No. Mama Patrick says "No."

27:09.128 --> 27:12.672
Patrick. It's Sam.
It's Sam speaking to you right now.

27:12.756 --> 27:14.507
I'm begging you to do this for me.

27:14.591 --> 27:15.258
I concede!

27:18.345 --> 27:19.554
