able to help Brad get sober.

30:33.332 --> 30:35.208
I asked Patrick if he felt sad...

30:35.292 --> 30:38.127
that he still had to keep it a secret.

30:38.212 --> 30:40.922
And he said "No," because at least now...

30:41.006 --> 30:44.717
