34:05.502 --> 34:07.920
I'll help you study for the next one.

34:08.004 --> 34:09.505
Will you?

34:09.589 --> 34:10.840
Yeah. Of course.

34:12.134 --> 34:13.676
Thanks, Charlie.

34:26.148 --> 34:27.565
What's this?

34:27.649 --> 34:31.235
It’s just a mix tape. No big deal.

34:31.319 --> 34:33.279
My parents have a good stereo, so...

34:34.989 --> 34:37.449
