this person across the room.

35:19.284 --> 35:21.452
And from that moment, I'd know...

35:21.536 --> 35:24.246
everything was going to be okay.

35:25.707 --> 35:27.041
You know what I mean?

35:29.211 --> 35:30.294
Yeah.

35:46.561 --> 35:48.229
I hope it works out.

35:48.313 --> 35:50.231
