35:56.238 --> 35:59.490
I just hope she can stop playing dumb
with these guys.

35:59.574 --> 36:03.118
I keep telling her, "Don't
make yourself small."

36:04.162 --> 36:05.913
Can't save anybody.

36:07.290 --> 36:08.749
Excuse me.

36:08.834 --> 36:11.377
Man, your mix is morbidly sad, kid.

36:11.461 --> 36:13.921
How about something
a little bit more upbeat?

36:14.005 --> 36:15.714
Let’s just see.

36:15.799 --> 36:17.925
So Sam tells me you wanna be a writer.

36:19.803 --> 36:21.053
Yeah.

36:21.137 --> 36:22.429
