38:07.285 --> 38:10.579
Page 291 in your book.

38:12.040 --> 38:14.208
And I ordered you some breakfast.

38:14.292 --> 38:16.085
The country breakfast.

38:32.727 --> 38:34.186
Dad?

38:34.270 --> 38:36.397
Can I have 30 dollars?

38:36.481 --> 38:38.649
