What do you need 10 dollars for?

38:38.733 --> 38:40.025
Sam's doing Secret Santa.

38:40.110 --> 38:42.403
It's her favorite thing in the world.
Please?

38:45.365 --> 38:46.490
Have fun.

38:48.743 --> 38:49.910
Thanks.

39:02.132 --> 39:03.507
Charlie.

39:03.591 --> 39:06.343
This was my favorite book growing up.

39:06.428 --> 39:09.680
This is my copy, but I want you to have it.

39:11.099 --> 39:12.391
Thanks.

39:12.475 --> 39:13.851
Have a great Christmas break.

39:13.935 --> 39:15.686
You, too, Mr. Anderson.

39:18.690 --> 39:19.773
Terrible stain.

39:22.944 --> 39:26.780
That's pretty good, Charlie.

39:33.371 --> 39:34.830
