Ladies and gentlemen, I am below average!

39:48.678 --> 39:51.055
- Below average!
- Below average!

39:51.139 --> 39:52.723
Guys, 1210.

39:52.807 --> 39:53.849
What?

39:55.351 --> 39:59.229
