40:34.933 --> 40:36.934
a Magnetic Poetry set...

40:37.018 --> 40:38.811
a book about Harvey Milk...

40:38.895 --> 40:43.565
and a mix tape with
the song "Asleep" on it twice.

40:43.650 --> 40:45.275
