41:00.500 --> 41:01.667
Obviously.

41:01.751 --> 41:02.876
Beautifully done.

41:02.961 --> 41:05.546
All right, Charlie. It's your turn.

41:06.297 --> 41:07.714
Okay.

41:07.799 --> 41:10.968
Okey dokey.

41:11.052 --> 41:17.558
I have received socks, pants,
