41:51.759 --> 41:53.093
Wait a second.

41:53.178 --> 41:55.179
There's only Secret Santa presents.
There's rules.

41:55.263 --> 41:58.390
Mary Elizabeth, why are you
trying to eat Christmas?

41:58.474 --> 41:59.766
Hand them out, Sam.

41:59.851 --> 42:02.769
All right. Mary Elizabeth. For you.

42:03.771 --> 42:04.771
Alice.

42:04.856 --> 42:06.023
