42:22.373 --> 42:23.999
He really knows me.

42:39.349 --> 42:41.225
All right, Charlie.

42:41.976 --> 42:43.060
Come on out.

42:43.144 --> 42:44.269
Get out here, buddy.

42:44.354 --> 42:45.479
Come on, Charlie. Charlie!

42:46.648 --> 42:48.982
Don't be shy.

42:49.067 --> 42:51.777
Come out, come out, wherever...

42:59.244 --> 43:00.911
Yeah!

43:00.995 --> 43:05.332
