43:43.079 --> 43:44.413
You don't have to say anything.

44:05.560 --> 44:08.145
I'm really sorry we can't
be here for your birthday.

44:08.229 --> 44:11.481
No, that's okay. I'm just sorry
you have to go back and visit your dad.

44:11.566 --> 44:14.318
I'm in such a good mood
I don't think even he could ruin it.

44:14.402 --> 44:16.820
I feel like I'm finally doing good.

44:16.904 --> 44:18.030
You are.

44:18.114 --> 44:20.907
Well, what about you?

44:20.992 --> 44:24.745
When I met you,
you were this scared freshman.

44:25.913 --> 44:27.414
Now look at you in that suit.

44:27.498 --> 44:30.834
You're like a sexy English schoolboy.

44:30.918 --> 44:32.336
I saw Mary Elizabeth checking you out.

44:32.420 --> 44:33.378
No.

44:34.088 --> 44:36.006
Innocent.

44:36.090 --> 44:37.507
Worst kinda guys.

44:37.592 --> 44:38.759
Never see you coming.

44:38.843 --> 44:41.053
And parents love you.

44:41.137 --> 44:43.388
That's, like...

44:43.473 --> 44:45.057
extra danger.

44:45.141 --> 44:47.184
Yeah, well, it hasn't worked so far.

44:47.268 --> 44:49.269
You've never had a girlfriend?

44:49.354 --> 44:51.438
Not even like a second grade Valentine?

44:51.522 --> 44:52.564
Nope.

44:52.648 --> 44:54.399
Have you ever kissed a girl?

44:54.484 --> 44:55.609
No.

44:56.819 --> 44:58.111
What about you?

45:01.991 --> 45:03.742
Have I ever kissed a girl?

45:03.826 --> 45:05.952
No, no. Your first kiss.

45:07.789 --> 45:09.706
I was 11.

45:09.791 --> 45:11.541
His name was Robert.

45:11.626 --> 45:13.919
He used to come over to
the house all the time.

45:14.003 --> 45:15.629
Was he your first boyfriend?

45:16.964 --> 45:19.049
He was my...

45:19.133 --> 45:21.301
He was my dad's boss.

45:24.222 --> 45:28.892
You know, Charlie, I used to sleep
with guys who treated me like shit.

45:28.976 --> 45:31.520
And get wasted all the time.

45:32.522 --> 45:33.980
But now I feel like...

45:34.899 --> 45:36.775
I have a chance. Like...

45:36.859 --> 45:39.152
I can even get into a real college.

45:39.237 --> 45:41.029
It's true. You can do it.

45:46.077 --> 45:47.786
You really think so?

45:52.041 --> 45:58.839
My aunt had that same thing
done to her, too.

45:58.923 --> 46:01.341
And she turned her life around.

46:03.010 --> 46:05.595
She must have been great.

46:05.680 --> 46:08.515
She was my favorite person in the world.

46:08.599 --> 46:09.850
Until now.

46:18.109 --> 46:19.443
Charlie...

46:21.362 --> 46:26.366
I know that you know I like Craig.

46:26.451 --> 46:29.870
But I want to forget about that
for a minute, okay?

46:29.954 --> 46:31.788
Okay.

46:31.873 --> 46:36.042
I just wanna make sure
that the first person who kisses you...

46:36.878 --> 46:38.503
loves you.

46:38.588 --> 46:39.796
Okay?

46:43.468 --> 46:44.926
Okay.

47:03.404 --> 47:05.238
