47:29.805 --> 47:31.932
Because your birthday's on Christmas Eve...

47:32.016 --> 47:33.892
I figure you don't get that many presents?

47:35.436 --> 47:37.229
I thought you should have my clock.

47:37.313 --> 47:38.522
From the heart.

47:38.606 --> 47:40.357
Thank you, Patrick.

47:42.527 --> 47:43.777
