for Santa Claus.

48:39.959 --> 48:43.336
Why don't you keep an eye out for him,
and I will be right back, okay?

48:45.631 --> 48:48.508
Going to get your birthday present.

48:59.437 --> 49:03.148
Hey.

49:04.775 --> 49:07.277
God, I miss Mom's cooking.

49:07.361 --> 49:09.404
You have no idea how good you have it.

49:11.115 --> 49:13.325
I'm actually starting to hate pizza.

49:14.910 --> 49:16.411
So how you liking school?

49:16.495 --> 49:20.040
Well, I'm no braniac like you or Candace.

49:20.791 --> 49:22.334
I'm doing okay.

49:22.418 --> 49:24.419
Okay? You're playing in a bowl game.

49:32.887 --> 49:34.679
How are you feeling, Charlie?

49:37.016 --> 49:37.849
Good.

49:37.933 --> 49:39.809
No, you know what I mean.

49:40.603 --> 49:41.853
Is it bad tonight?

49:42.980 --> 49:45.690
No.

49:46.942 --> 49:49.903
I'm not picturing things anymore.

49:49.987 --> 49:53.114
Or if I do, I can just shut it off.

49:54.992 --> 49:58.662
Well, you know, Mom did say
that you have good friends now.

49:58.746 --> 50:02.290
