and it just lied to me.

51:33.215 --> 51:35.508
Okay, Charlie,
don't freak out. Give me this.

51:36.177 --> 51:37.469
Calm down.

51:41.390 --> 51:42.640
Look up.

51:45.311 --> 51:46.603
Isn't it quiet?

51:49.273 --> 51:52.192
Sam, do you think if people knew...

51:52.276 --> 51:55.779
how crazy you really were,
no one would ever talk to you?

51:57.865 --> 51:59.574
All the time.

52:03.454 --> 52:05.955
So you wanna wear these glasses?

52:08.209 --> 52:09.959
They'll protect you.

53:31.625 --> 53:34.711
10, 9, 8, 7...

53:34.795 --> 53:37.672
6, 5, 4...

53:37.756 --> 53:39.674
3, 2, 1!

53:39.758 --> 53:41.467
It's gonna be our little secret.

54:41.654 --> 54:43.529
Did your older friends pressure you?

54:43.614 --> 54:46.407
No one pressured me, Officer.

54:46.492 --> 54:49.953
I would never do drugs. Never.

54:50.037 --> 54:53.414
Then how did you happen to be passed out
on the ground at 6:00 in the morning?

54:55.125 --> 54:59.420
Well, I, um— I-I was really tired.

54:59.505 --> 55:02.507
And I was feeling feverish...

55:02.591 --> 55:07.303
so I went outside
for a walk just to get some cold air.

55:07.388 --> 55:09.806
I started seeing things, so I passed out.

55:09.890 --> 55:11.391
You're seeing things again, Charlie?

55:12.810 --> 55:14.686
Not really.

55:20.859 --> 55:22.360
Nice suit.

55:24.238 --> 55:26.030
It was a Christmas present.

55:30.744 --> 55:32.537
Did you have fun on your break?

55:32.621 --> 55:35.248
More fun than you're gonna
have today, Sinatra.

55:38.335 --> 55:39.794
Nice look, jag-off.

55:43.298 --> 55:45.008
I've called him 30 times.

55:45.092 --> 55:47.373
What are we supposed to do?
We're going on in 10 minutes.

55:48.679 --> 55:50.179
- They said in health class—
- Hello?

55:50.264 --> 55:52.348
They say that about
L.S.D.just to scare you.

55:52.433 --> 55:55.601
- Are you sure? You know I've seen—
- Charlie, you're fine, man.

55:55.686 --> 55:58.271
Guys, we have an emergency.

55:58.355 --> 55:59.981
