58:28.213 --> 58:30.756
- Please, come in.
- Okay.

58:30.841 --> 58:32.300
A little closer together.

58:32.384 --> 58:33.843
That looks nice.

58:33.927 --> 58:35.928
Buddhist, I need you to
smile a little bit more.

58:36.013 --> 58:37.763
There you go. Nice.

59:08.795 --> 59:10.129
Hey.

59:10.214 --> 59:11.631
Hey.

59:11.715 --> 59:13.216
Are you having a good time?

59:15.719 --> 59:19.138
Not really. How about you?

59:19.848 --> 59:21.682
I mean, I don't know.

59:21.767 --> 59:24.227
It's my first date, I don't
have much to compare it to.

59:24.853 --> 59:26.312
You're doing fine.

59:30.234 --> 59:33.402
Sorry Craig couldn't come.

59:33.487 --> 59:37.531
Yeah. He said he didn't want to go to
some stupid high school dance.

59:37.616 --> 59:40.534
I can't say I blame him really.

59:40.619 --> 59:43.996
I don't know.
If you like it, he should come.

59:49.253 --> 59:50.544
Thanks, Charlie.

59:53.423 --> 59:55.633
Have a beautiful first date.

59:55.717 --> 59:57.718
You deserve it.

59:57.803 --> 59:59.387
I'll try not to make you too jealous.

01:00:13.610 --> 01:00:15.111
Now just let it breathe.

01:00:24.162 --> 01:00:24.996
Whoa.

01:00:27.165 --> 01:00:29.000
