01:01:52.626 --> 01:01:54.377
Don't be nervous.

01:02:31.873 --> 01:02:33.165
Charlie.

01:02:36.253 --> 01:02:38.379
I didn't know how tonight
was gonna go, but...

01:02:39.923 --> 01:02:41.090
It's really nice, isn't it?

01:02:41.174 --> 01:02:42.508
Yeah.

01:02:44.553 --> 01:02:46.095
I just can't believe it.

01:02:47.264 --> 01:02:48.931
You, of all people.

01:02:49.015 --> 01:02:51.600
I just can't believe you're my boyfriend.

01:02:57.190 --> 01:02:59.358
Shit! My parents! Shit!

01:02:59.443 --> 01:03:01.610
- Here, zip this up.
- Okay. No, I got this.

01:03:01.695 --> 01:03:03.135
Just zip it up like a normal zipper!

01:03:03.196 --> 01:03:04.321
It's stuck. It’s just...

01:03:05.198 --> 01:03:06.824
Thank you.

01:03:06.908 --> 01:03:08.033
See you Monday.

01:03:09.369 --> 01:03:11.954
Dear friend...

01:03:12.038 --> 01:03:15.207
sorry I haven't written for a while...

01:03:15.292 --> 01:03:17.877
but things are a total disaster.

01:03:19.212 --> 01:03:21.839
We're literally making
out and I'm in my bra...

01:03:21.923 --> 01:03:23.507
Hello!
And the front door opens, it's my parents!

01:03:23.592 --> 01:03:25.801
I probably should have been honest about...

01:03:25.886 --> 01:03:28.971
how I didn't want to go out with
Mary Elizabeth after Sadie's, but...

01:03:29.055 --> 01:03:31.307
I really didn't want to hurt her feelings.

01:03:32.559 --> 01:03:35.478
You see, Mary Elizabeth
is a really nice person...

01:03:35.562 --> 01:03:37.855
underneath the part of
her that hates everyone.

01:03:37.939 --> 01:03:39.523
Hey!

01:03:39.608 --> 01:03:41.275
And since I heard that
having a girlfriend makes you happy...

01:03:41.359 --> 01:03:43.861
I tried hard to love her like I love Sam.

